{"title":"The best Apple Cyber Monday deals still available","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/541154/cyber-monday-apple-deals.html","date":1638364824000,"content":"<div>\n<section><div></div></section><p>No longer is Black Friday limited to the day after Thanksgiving—holiday shopping deals began as soon as the summer ended and they won’t stop until Santa arrives. But searching for the best Apple deals doesn’t have to be an overwhelming, stressful experience. If you’re patient and smart, you can save big on Apple products without needing to wait in the cold or battle people for doorbusters.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cyber Week 2021: Deals on every Apple product</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Black Friday and Cyber Monday Apple deals are going strong. Here are the best sales we’ve tracked so far:</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/airpods3-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" /></figure><p>Jason Cross / IDG</p></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cyber Week AirPods Deals</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09JQL3NWT/?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">AirPods (3rd-gen): $150</a> ($29 off)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09JQMJHXY/?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">AirPods Pro: $197</a> ($52 off)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08PZJN7BD?ots=1&amp;tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/article/549669/apple-black-friday-2021-airpods-deals-expect.html\"></a><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/New-Apple-AirPods-Max-Silver/dp/B08PZHYWJS/?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">AirPods Max: $479</a> ($80 off)</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/iphone-13-front.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" /></figure><p>Michael Simon/IDG</p></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cyber Week iPhone Deals</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/